RE: Does Christian Religion etc? Those are good points with regard to religious households but the fact still remains that women have more options than children. And the younger the child, the fewer options he/she has. In fact, children are treated more as property than they are sovereign human beings, which is deplorable.
In the end, a woman (or a man) has options that a child simply does not.
